name: Sensor Web Server Helgoland API v3.1.0
body:
Available in [Maven Central](https://search.maven.org/search?q=g:org.n52.sensorweb-server.helgoland%20and%20v:3.1.0).

## Change Log 

* Update URLs from http to https
* Add badges
* Fix lgtm issues with invalid number of arguments in log statement

### Dependency Updates

* Bump parent from 16 to 18 (#492)
* Bump spring-boot-dependencies from 2.2.4.RELEASE to 2.2.5.RELEASE (#494)
* Bump jackson-annotations from 2.10.2 to 2.10.3 (#495)
* Bump spotbugs-annotations from 4.0.0 to 4.0.1 (#498)
* Bump version.junit from 5.6.0 to 5.6.1 (#499)
* Bump spring-boot-dependencies from 2.2.5.RELEASE to 2.2.6.RELEASE (#500)
* Bump arctic-sea.version from 7.3.0 to 7.3.1 (#497)
* Bump arctic-sea.version from 7.3.1 to 7.4.0 (#501)


### Breaking Changes

See [here](https://github.com/52North/sensorweb-server-helgoland/compare/v3.0.0...v3.1.0) for the complete commit log.
